1. **Manifest declarations:** Your new `conversations:set-title` call is already declared in the manifest (line 143 of conversations/src/plugin.ts). If you fire a new event (e.g., `chat:title-updated`), do NOT add it to `registers` or `calls` — only `subscribes` goes in the manifest. The firing plugin never declares what it fires.

